Tech |first1=Simon |title=Winners - Young Artist Awards |url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/winners |website=www.youngartistawards.org |accessdate=April 7, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018\n| [[44th Saturn Awards|Saturn Awards]]\n| Best Horror Television Series\n| ''Teen Wolf''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-nominations-2018-black-panther-walking-dead-1202727752/ |title='Black Panther,' 'Walking Dead' Rule Saturn Awards Nominations |last=McNary |first=Dave |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=March 15, 2018 |accessdate=March 15, 2018 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6xwc1azco?url=http://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-nominations-2018-black-panther-walking-dead-1202727752/ |archivedate=March 15, 2018 |url-status=live |df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Broadcast==\nCanada's [[MuchMusic]] aired the series until 2014,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.muchmusic.com/tv/teenwolf/ |title=Teen Wolf (S.3 Pt.2) &#124; Hallway Promo |website=Muchmusic.com |accessdate=December 4, 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108034701/http://www.muchmusic.com/tv/teenwolf/ |archivedate=January 8, 2014 |df=mdy-all }}</ref> when it was moved to the domestic version of [[MTV (Canadian TV channel)|MTV]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://bellmediapr.ca/Network/MTV/Press/MTV-Howls-Its-Way-to-the-Winter-Premiere-of-TEEN-WOLF |title=MTV Howls Its Way to the Winter Premiere of TEEN WOLF and the Debut of New After-Show WOLF WATCH, Jan. 6}}</ref> The United Kingdom's [[BSkyB]] aired the first two seasons on [[pay television]] channel [[Sky Living]]. BSkyB stopped broadcasting ''Teen Wolf'' after the second-season finale.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvwise.co.uk/2013/05/la-screenings-sky-living-drops-mtvs-drama-series-teen-wolf/ |title=LA Screenings: Sky Living Drops MTV's Drama Series 'Teen Wolf' |first=Patrick |last=Munn |date=May 20, 2013 |website=TV Wise}}</ref>\n\n==Bibliography==\n* J. Elliott & M. Fowler, \u201cSmile, Dere